'''飓风巴里'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Barry}}）是[[1983年大西洋飓风季|1983年大西洋飓风季]]的第4个热带低气压、第2场获得命名的风暴和第2场飓风。系统源于8月23日的一股[[东风波|东风波]]，在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]近海迅速增强，达到风速每小时95公里的第一波强度高峰。但由于[[风切变|风切变]]增多，气旋又减弱成热带低气压，再于次日早上从佛罗里达州[[墨尔本_(佛罗里达州)|墨尔本]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。巴里朝接近正西方向移动，强度得以恢复，于8月28日升级成飓风。当晚，气旋以最高强度从墨西哥北部沿海地区登陆，然后就开始快速弱化，于次日消散。

受飓风影响，墨西哥北部有数以百计的民居被毁，导致400余人无家可归，但没有任何报道表明风暴曾造成人员丧生，损失数额也缺乏统计。此外，气旋对美国的影响很小。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Barry 1983 track.png}}
1983年8月13日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，由于大西洋盆地存在强烈[[风切变|风切变]]，系统起初无法得到显著发展，关联的[[对流|对流]]也很少。8月22日逼近[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]期间，有[[低压槽|上层低压槽]]逐渐同系统拉开距离，风切变因此减少。<ref name="MWS">{{cite report | author1 = Robert A. Case | author2 = Harold P. Gerrish | date = 1984-05 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1983 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193724/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1983.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1983.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]进入后，系统催生出[[低气压|低气压区]]并得到强化。8月23日，低气压区的组织已有显著改善，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此将之归类为[[1983年大西洋飓风季|本季]]第四号热带低气压。当晚，低气压迅速增强成热带风暴并获名“巴里”（{{lang|en|Barry}}）<ref name="BarryPg1">{{cite report | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | year = 1983 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Barry – Page 1 – Storm History | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002023819/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim01.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-10-02}}</ref><ref name="TDN1">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''The Deseret News'' | date = 1983-08-24 | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | title = Tropical Storm Barry Heading for Cocoa Beach | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=luUOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EYMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5118,2875213&dq=tropical-storm-barry&hl=zh-CN | archive-date = 2021-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210405200739/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=luUOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EYMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5118%2C2875213&dq=tropical-storm-barry&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref>。成为热带风暴约12小时后，巴里的风速达到每小时95公里，登上第一波强度高峰<ref name="BarryPg3">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1983 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Barry – Page 3 – Preliminary Best Track | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203630/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim03.gif}}</ref>。

气旋接下来开始向西侧的[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]中部逼近，但由于风切变逐渐增多，系统随即减弱。8月25日，美国国家飓风中心又把巴里降级成热带低气压。<ref name="BarryPg1" />8月24日，系统以风力时速55公里强度从佛罗里达州[[墨尔本_(佛罗里达州)|墨尔本]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="BarryPg3" />。经过佛罗里达州后，低气压在强烈上层气流的影响下朝西南偏西方向前进。8月27日，由于行经洋面风切变减少，外界环境更趋利好，巴里的结构已有显著改善，因此在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]中部再度升级成热带风暴。气旋朝几乎正西方向逼近[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]，组织结构继续加强。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]次日中午12点，巴里在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[布朗斯维尔_(德克萨斯州)|布朗斯维尔]]东南方向约120公里海域升级成飓风。风暴继续增强，以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]130公里的最高强度从布朗斯维尔东南偏南方向约55公里处登陆。<ref name="BarryPg1" /><ref name="BarryPg3" />进入陆地上空后，气旋迅速弱化，次日便在墨西哥北部上空消散<ref name="BarryPg1" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Barry_(1983).JPG|right]]

=== 美国 ===
面对风暴威胁，佛罗里达州和德克萨斯州沿海地区接获多份[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告或观察预警]]<ref name="BarryPg4">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1983 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Barry – Page 4 – Watches and Warnings | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215333/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim04.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim04.gif | format = GIF}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月24日下午19点，佛罗里达州[[丘比特入口殖民地_(佛罗里达州)|丘比特入口殖民地]]到[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]之间地区首先接获[[热带气旋警告|烈风警告]]。次日，[[圣奥古斯汀_(佛罗里达州)|圣奥古斯汀]]（{{lang|en|St. Augustine}}）到萨凡纳之间的烈风警告中止。8月27日，德克萨斯州布朗斯维尔到[[奥康纳港_(德克萨斯州)|奥康纳港]]（{{lang|en|Port O'Connor}}）之间区域收到烈风警告，再随巴里增强而在数小时后升级成飓风警告，警告范围还延伸到[[曼斯菲尔德_(德克萨斯州)|曼斯菲尔德]]（{{lang|en|Mansfield}}），直到8月28晚中止<ref name="BarryPg4" />。为防万一，[[南帕诸岛|南帕诸岛]]（{{lang|en|South Padre Island}}）有4000余人撤离<ref name="BarryPg2">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1983 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Barry – Page 2 – Meteorological Statisitics and Impact | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim02.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223110/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1983-prelim/barry/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF}}</ref>。随着飓风逼近，[[努埃塞斯县_(得克萨斯州)|努埃塞斯县]]的[[阿兰萨斯港_(德克萨斯州)|阿兰萨斯港]]（{{lang|en|Port Aransas}}）多个海滩在8月27日有数千人疏散。估计布朗斯维尔有约700人前往避难所暂避，[[哈灵根_(德克萨斯州)|哈灵根]]另有约800人躲进充当临时避难所的学校，哈灵根此外还有2000居民撤离。[[卡梅伦县_(得克萨斯州)|卡梅伦县]]的[[圣贝尼托_(德克萨斯州)|圣贝尼托]]（{{lang|en|San Benito}}）、[[圣罗莎_(德克萨斯州)|圣罗莎]]（{{lang|en|Santa Rosa}}）和[[洛斯弗雷斯诺斯_(德克萨斯州)|洛斯弗雷斯诺斯]]（{{lang|en|Los Fresnos}}）均有开设避难所。<ref name="PPG1">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = ''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette'' | date = 1983-08-29 | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | title = Hurricane Barry Loses Punch in Mexico | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=gk4NAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pm0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=4527,6524964&dq=hurricane+barry&hl=zh-CN | archive-date = 2021-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210405200820/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=gk4NAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pm0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=4527%2C6524964&dq=hurricane+barry&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref>此外，[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]还有多个石油平台疏散<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = ''The Post-Standard'' | date = 1983-08-29 | title = Hurricane Fizzles Before Reaching Populated Areas Along Texas Coast}}</ref>。

=== 墨西哥 ===
位于德克萨斯州以南的墨西哥[[塔毛利帕斯州|塔毛利帕斯州]][[马塔莫罗斯_(塔毛利帕斯州)|马塔莫罗斯市]]经广播向市民发布飓风逼近的消息，许多人离开沿海村落前往内陆<ref name="PPG1" />。面对风暴威胁，墨西哥政府还将警戒级别提升到三级<ref name="THA1">{{cite news | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | publisher = ''Logansport Pharos-Tribune'' | date = 1983-08-29 | title = Barry Blows Out of South Texas}}</ref>。

== 影响和善后 ==
[[File:Barry_1983_rainfall.png|thumb]]

=== 美国 ===
[[奥基乔比湖|奥基乔比湖]]周边地区的降雨量约为25毫米，[[奥兰多_(佛罗里达州)|奥兰多]]周边地区则有76.2毫米，迈阿密地区也是25毫米。[[沃楚拉_(佛罗里达州)|沃楚拉]]巴里在美国产生降水最多的所在，达76.5毫米。<ref name="BarryRain">{{cite report | author = David Roth | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall: Hurricane Barry | publisher = Hydrometeorogical Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/barry1983.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210402072905/https://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/barry1983.html | date =  | archive-date = 2021-04-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[基韦斯特_(佛罗里达州)|基韦斯特]]降下38.1毫米雨量，导致多条排水不畅的道路被淹<ref name="News6">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 1983-08-26 | title = Rain Transforms Street Into Lake | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB35D5B0DE77734&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | newspaper = ''The Miami Herald'' | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | archive-date = 2021-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210405200808/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB35D5B0DE77734&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。巴里还对[[挑战者号航天飞机|挑战者号航天飞机]]的发射构成影响，{{lang|en|[[STS-8|STS-8]]}}任务原订于8月30日启动。[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]没有足够的时间赶在风暴来袭前将航天飞机运回机库，所以挑战号最终是停在发射台上经受气旋洗礼。<ref name="News5">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = NASA Secures Shuttle As Storm Heads for Cape Canaveral | publisher = ''The Miami Herald'' | date = 1983-08-25 | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PI&s_site=philly&p_multi=PI&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB296072B9572DA&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2021-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210405200823/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PI&s_site=philly&p_multi=PI&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB296072B9572DA&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>德克萨斯州只有[[圣安东尼奥_(德克萨斯州)|圣安东尼奥]]周边因巴里降下约25毫米雨量<ref name="BarryRain" />。该州海岸沿线的浪高比正常水平高0.3至0.6米，造成一定程度的海滩侵蚀<ref name="BarryPg2" />。南帕诸岛近海的阵风时速超过85公里<ref name="BarryPg2" />，布朗斯维尔附近可能出现[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，导致多条输电线缆中断，约有6000人因此失去供电<ref name="THA1" />。

=== 墨西哥 ===
没有任何报道表明巴里曾造成人员伤亡，但飓风还是导致墨西哥数百户民居被毁，另有30艘渔船沉没，导致400余人流离失所，捕虾网受到严重破坏，该国多个渔村测得0.9至1.2米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="BarryPg2" />。风暴产生的降水缓解了墨西哥北部部分地区的旱情<ref name="BarryPg1" />，梅斯基塔尔（{{lang|en|El Mezquital}}）有至少10人无家可归。圣特雷莎（{{lang|en|Santa Teresa}}）有多户民房受到一定程度破坏，但还不至被毁<ref name="TPS1">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = ''The Post-Standard'' | date = 1983-08-29 | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | title = Hurricane Fizzles Before Reaching Populated Areas Along Texas Coast | url = http://newspaperarchive.com/us/new-york/syracuse/syracuse-post-standard/1983/08-29/page-8 | archive-date = 2016-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160407030259/http://newspaperarchive.com/us/new-york/syracuse/syracuse-post-standard/1983/08-29/page-8 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。有一名孩童被破碎窗户的玻璃割伤<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = ''The Paris News'' | date = 1983-08-30 | title = About 400 Homeless After Hurricane Barry}}</ref>。风暴过去后，军方领导人领导医疗队前往塔毛利帕斯州评估破坏程度<ref name="PPG1" />。

